Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,===========OP================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.79,0:01:13.35,OP,,0,0,0,,このあたりイチバン見晴らしの良いあの木に登って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.50,0:01:21.03,OP,,0,0,0,,あの子が笑う 無邪気に笑う 夢を見る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.54,0:01:45.42,OP,,0,0,0,,空を泳いだ魚の向こうじっと目を凝らせば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.73,0:01:52.42,OP,,0,0,0,,町の隅っこ色褪せてゆく日々がある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.70,0:01:56.63,OP,,0,0,0,,ゆびきりしたままで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.66,0:01:59.60,OP,,0,0,0,,サヨナラしても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.74,0:02:08.60,OP,,0,0,0,,果たされる日を待ってこの木に宿るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.50,0:02:12.71,OP,,0,0,0,,何回も繰り返す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:16.88,OP,,0,0,0,,そのたび涙する
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.50,0:02:20.50,OP,,0,0,0,,止まって動き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:24.90,OP,,0,0,0,,そのすべてを確かめるように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:32.96,OP,,0,0,0,,ほら やまびこが聞こえるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.79,0:01:13.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an2}爬上這一帶視野最美的那棵樹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.50,0:01:21.03,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an2}孩子笑了 笑得天真無邪 她看到了夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.54,0:01:45.42,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an2}定定地盯著空中暢游的魚兒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.73,0:01:52.42,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an2}小鎮每個角落裡漸漸褪色的日子浮現出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.70,0:01:56.63,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an2}拉鉤上吊百年不變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.66,0:01:59.60,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an2}即使分開了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.74,0:02:08.60,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an2}等待約定實現的心情也寄託在這顆樹上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.50,0:02:12.71,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an2}一遍一遍地重複
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:16.88,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an2}每次都止不住淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.50,0:02:20.50,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an2}停下來又繼續走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:24.90,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an2}彷彿是要印證這一切似的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:32.96,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an2}山間回音響不絕 你說是不是呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,===========ED================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.64,0:22:25.16,ED,,0,0,0,,夜の水面に飛び交う蛍が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.35,0:22:30.02,ED,,0,0,0,,流れ星みたいできれーなのん
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.31,0:22:34.67,ED,,0,0,0,,どこからともない雉鳩の声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:39.47,ED,,0,0,0,,モノマネしながらいく でこぼこ道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.73,0:22:43.89,ED,,0,0,0,,澄み渡る星空の下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.18,0:22:49.87,ED,,0,0,0,,いつのまにか並んで眠ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.31,0:22:57.47,ED,,0,0,0,,朝日がおかえりって微笑んでた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.68,0:23:07.40,ED,,0,0,0,,ここは世界一優しい おかえりが待ってる場所
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.66,0:23:12.11,ED,,0,0,0,,さりげない日常 ふわりと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.34,0:23:16.16,ED,,0,0,0,,抱きしめてくれるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.48,0:23:26.22,ED,,0,0,0,,ここは世界一暖かい 春が訪れる場所
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.52,0:23:37.33,ED,,0,0,0,,ほら 花のこえが聞こえてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.64,0:22:25.16,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}夜晚的水面上飛來飛去的螢火蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.35,0:22:30.02,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}就像是流星一般好美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.31,0:22:34.67,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不知何處傳來了雉鳩的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:39.47,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}踏著凹凸不平的小路 邊走邊玩模仿秀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.73,0:22:43.89,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我們在繁星遍佈的澄空下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.18,0:22:49.87,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不知不覺就並排著睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.31,0:22:57.47,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}朝陽微笑著歡迎我們回家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.68,0:23:07.40,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}這裡是全世界最美好的地方 是有人等待我們回家的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.66,0:23:12.11,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那些平平淡淡的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.34,0:23:16.16,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}輕輕地擁抱我們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.48,0:23:26.22,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}這裡是全世界最溫暖的地方 是春天到訪的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.52,0:23:37.33,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}豎起耳朵來 能聽到花兒的聲音喔
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,===========Story================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是一條螢 小學五年級生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.50,0:00:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個春天 轉學來到了這間小小的分校
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我叫一條螢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.53,0:00:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來自東京
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.28,0:00:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 從東京過來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個字讀螢呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.46,0:00:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.89,0:00:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼年級呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小五
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.46,0:00:44.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比我小 比我小嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.58,0:00:46.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看著不像小五呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在之前的學校闖禍了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.28,0:00:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是爸爸工作的緣故…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 很普通呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.99,0:01:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喵帕斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.55,0:01:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喵… 喵…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(OP)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:38.51,title,NTP,0,0,0,,去\N看\N星\N星\N了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轉學過來之後 轉眼就過了幾天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.02,0:02:48.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡和以前的學校有很多不一樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都會吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:02:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同一間教室裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有初二的小鞠前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.91,0:02:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有初一的夏海前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:02:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有小一的蓮華醬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有小鞠前輩和夏海前輩的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 螢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來玩撞尺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.22,0:03:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撞尺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.26,0:03:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是用尺玩的遊戲啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 我完全沒聽說過 如果那樣也沒問題的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK OK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿尺和筆過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一邊玩一邊說明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在小夏的家玩過 所以也來說明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對準對手的尺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:33.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它撞出桌面就贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那螢先來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.28,0:03:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.12,0:03:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 壓到上面了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 那樣沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果把對手的尺壓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.57,0:03:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對手彈三次沒辦法脫離的話就輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.19,0:03:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次是螢的尺把蓮醬的壓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮醬彈三次沒辦法脫離的話 蓮醬就輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fad(500,500)\bord6\3c&H84D052&\pos(640,456)}彈三次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:04:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fad(500,500)\bord6\3c&H84D052&\pos(640,456)}脫離就安全
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fad(500,500)\bord6\3c&H84D052&\pos(640,456)}脫離不了就出局
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.95,0:04:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣呀 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢 別這麼快就以為贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.70,0:04:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有注意到這尺是怎麼放的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼放…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很普通吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.91,0:04:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是說比較窄有刻度的一面朝下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.34,0:04:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而這意味著什麼 現在就讓你見識一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.86,0:04:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是鯉躍龍門
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥 鯉躍龍門
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用筆敲擊尺較薄的地方讓尺跳起來的絕招
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是幾年前影姐命名的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是絕招名字呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就可以脫離被壓的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還可以反過來把別人壓住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著該我了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.49,0:04:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.64,0:05:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣蓮醬就只能用燕子翻身了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.68,0:05:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要用燕子翻身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 燕子翻身是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燕子翻身是在尺的一部分突出桌子的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.57,0:05:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用筆頂著尺移動把對手壓住的絕招
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反擊成功
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功脫離
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.91,0:05:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒打贏小小鞠呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 別叫我小小鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別人都叫你小小鞠嗎 前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人叫前輩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海和蓮華都不把我當成前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.55,0:05:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好新鮮的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也覺得好新鮮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和初中的前輩在同一間教室玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩位 很抱歉打擾到你們的快樂時光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實為了今天我已經把尺改造過了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.30,0:05:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尺的兩面已經上好蠟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣降低摩擦力之後 就能使出更高級的招式了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就能把姐姐踢出局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了呀前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不過 這麼滑的話很容易會自殺 沒問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:12.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就只有現在能這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼姐姐 覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好危險 從上面過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:20.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠟上太多了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看我就說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.23,0:06:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上蠟就是在自殺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.66,0:06:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是自己偷偷改造的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢 把夏海的尺撞下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:31.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.67,0:06:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那接下來就開始我的有如破竹的進攻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮華也覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次輪到我的時候 就要把剛才燕子翻身的仇報了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 輪到我了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.99,0:06:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 我的尺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 我手滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.15,0:06:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥也過來玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撞尺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.53,0:06:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐已經輸了 你可以頂她的位置中途加入哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:07:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那速度開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什… 一次攻擊把三人都打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 哥哥好強
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮醬 我們不合作的話就沒法贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一次攻擊就把他撞下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 把哥哥的尺撞下去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空 空手奪白刃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空手奪白刃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:32.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尺被撞出去之後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰到地板之前 用筆把它彈回桌面的救命絕招
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.86,0:07:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是高級絕招呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說哥哥是什麼時候移動過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 移到正中間確保安全
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好危險
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:54.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易回到安全地帶了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.48,0:08:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了贏哥哥 我要全部託付給小夏去賭一把了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥 你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.97,0:08:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到就能明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鯉躍龍門是使出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.91,0:08:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這不是壓在夏海上面了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.73,0:08:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了呀 蓮醬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.67,0:08:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣帶著蓮醬的尺 燕子翻身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.16,0:08:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩把尺一起壓住哥哥的尺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.35,0:08:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼艱難才兩把一起壓上去的 馬上就脫離了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題 這樣就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才只是為了逼哥哥逃到桌子邊上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來就輪到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡輕輕推一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.51,0:08:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼不撞它下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能在這裡撞下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 哥哥已經準備好使出空手奪白刃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 螢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那邊用力打過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的尺 蓮醬的尺和哥哥的尺一起撞下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:08:58.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:09:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不那樣就沒辦法贏哥哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海的尺在哥哥的尺上面滑出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.47,0:09:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 我的尺上蠟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.09,0:09:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後當哥哥被我那把高速飛出去的尺吸引住的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮醬的尺和哥哥的尺一起自爆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.57,0:09:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就三人合力 封印住空手接白刃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合力贏過哥哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.52,0:09:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢 撞尺感覺怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.27,0:09:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再來一次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來我想試試一個人能達到什麼程度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.34,0:10:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那再來打一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.43,0:10:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我要拿第一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.16,0:10:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息時間早就已經完了…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,(Partb)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.96,0:10:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒想到用筆和尺就能玩得那麼興奮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有彈橡皮擦之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彈橡皮擦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是用手指彈橡皮擦 把對手的橡皮擦撞出去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.35,0:10:37.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用筆和橡皮擦還能打棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還打過高爾夫球呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高爾夫球嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.88,0:10:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是高爾夫球場
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想玩一下 高爾夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下個星期一我們一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.76,0:10:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會練習的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有這麼多沒玩過的遊戲好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.37,0:11:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搬家到這裡之後 體驗到好多的第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:04.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 下次要去看星星嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個能看到很多星星的山丘哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.76,0:11:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.15,0:11:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.72,0:11:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那這個星期六怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,(Partb)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.02,0:11:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩奇 去散步了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖 乖 不要這麼急啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.03,0:11:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那出門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 去把前輩的筆記還了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.85,0:11:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高爾夫球昨天也玩過了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天氣真好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.21,0:11:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個天氣能看到星星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這條路沒走過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.40,0:11:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 佩奇 走一下看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.64,0:12:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩奇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.81,0:12:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.21,0:12:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是從哪條路走過來的來著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是從中間那條路來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 走錯了就回頭走另一邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 這是剛才的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走回原位的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說走左邊那條路就可以了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:13:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪 剛才過來的時候有看到河嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,徹底迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.79,0:13:11.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\pos(356,612)\frz3.33\c&HFEFDFF&}購物商城
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼地方呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎怎怎 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不認識路了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想問路也找不到人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.54,0:13:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰來救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.34,0:13:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鞠前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.70,0:13:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:40.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩奇 那是小鞠前輩的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.41,0:13:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩奇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.94,0:13:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩奇 要去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:46.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩奇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.33,0:13:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很危險的 快回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩奇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.34,0:13:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩奇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩奇
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,(Partb)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這條路一直走下去就可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真心對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算是回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.02,0:14:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.34,0:14:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要去看星星 其實到時候還也行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.30,0:14:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要亂逛 早點回來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是去看星星而已 很快就回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.39,0:14:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小螢 你要看著小鞠 不要讓她亂跑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.11,0:14:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:54.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 明明我的歲數更大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 夏海前輩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海吃完晚飯就睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮華的奶奶來了 所以她來不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是那樣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.27,0:15:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變成兩個人了 不過那樣也好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.45,0:15:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 哥哥把筆記給我了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.58,0:15:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.96,0:15:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有帶手電筒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.78,0:15:22.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題 我帶了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.39,0:15:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.50,0:15:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走這邊沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天白天我迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.05,0:15:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.71,0:15:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過現在有我在 沒問題哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.68,0:15:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有帶錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.49,0:15:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那買些果汁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.02,0:15:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在晚上買東西 感覺就像是大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.97,0:15:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.51,0:15:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般自動販賣機在晚上 都是蟲子天堂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.27,0:15:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般都這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:16:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我要橙汁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總感覺裡面有蟲子青蛙之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面有什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.11,0:16:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又濕又涼的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.27,0:16:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是果汁嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.43,0:16:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是果汁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.86,0:16:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果汁好好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒碰到蟲子太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不要跟媽媽說我買果汁了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.43,0:16:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被她知道我晚上買東西吃的話肯定會生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.33,0:16:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.70,0:16:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓶蓋掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 找不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.58,0:16:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變成路邊垃圾了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也來找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能花太多時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回來的時候再找會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.45,0:17:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那座山丘還有很遠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.98,0:17:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經走到沒有路燈的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.06,0:17:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺有點可…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…怕什麼的才不會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:24.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.36,0:17:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.53,0:17:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要拿著手電筒跑開哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有手電筒也沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是怕跑開的螢不小心摔倒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.54,0:17:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個… 謝謝關心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.05,0:17:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.56,0:17:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懂星座嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:17:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是獵戶座嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:08.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獵戶座好像是冬天的星座吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那仙女座是哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.56,0:18:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到認識的星星了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊的星星連起來就是拉麵座
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那那邊的連起來就是素麵座了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不回去的話媽媽就要生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺還沒看夠呢 下次再來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.49,0:18:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我照著腳下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.27,0:18:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢 為什麼把燈關了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.05,0:18:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 我沒有關呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它自己關的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我給我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點開開關…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.34,0:18:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開不了 好像是電池沒電了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.87,0:18:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.58,0:19:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.35,0:19:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.36,0:19:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢 螢你哭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.32,0:19:11.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這樣就哭了可不行… 不行呀 呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.71,0:19:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 太黑了 看不到回去的路呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要看看周圍的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.65,0:19:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.51,0:19:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會平安把螢送回家的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不要走開哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前 前輩認識路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不認識
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過也不能一直留在這
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.02,0:19:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢 注意腳下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要摔倒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:19:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 好像是從這邊來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.38,0:20:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我覺得好像是從這邊來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周圍只能看見樹影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.01,0:20:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪邊看起來都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果走錯方向的話就更加找不到路了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:17.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛也慢慢適應了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.34,0:20:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深呼吸冷靜下來的話肯定能找到路的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.25,0:20:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前 前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.71,0:20:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛 剛才那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.18,0:20:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蟲子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:32.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手拿到了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是瓶蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.49,0:20:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是剛才掉的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.52,0:20:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這邊這條路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.95,0:20:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 應該是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢 這邊 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前輩 那邊 能看到有光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.99,0:21:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們回來了哦 前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.63,0:21:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一放鬆下來就站不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.33,0:21:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.65,0:21:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實不用背我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.06,0:21:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是前輩幫我的謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.31,0:21:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站不住這事 千萬不能跟夏海說呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.40,0:21:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.58,0:21:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮華也不要說呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.63,0:21:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰都不要說呀 絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.37,0:21:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會當成我們兩個人之間的祕密的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,(Partb)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.64,0:21:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把尺擦得閃閃發亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.51,0:21:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害的樣子 不過這有意義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.47,0:21:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣絕對能贏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.21,0:21:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢 來玩撞尺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.35,0:21:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.62,0:22:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我脫胎換骨了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.24,0:21:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天不能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.56,0:22:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天一定贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.91,0:22:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會輸…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(trailer)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.55,0:23:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教我學英語
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.68,0:23:45.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,披薩 披薩 披薩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.32,0:23:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能衝動！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.55,0:23:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋糕！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.00,0:23:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不知火橘子
